  -------- --------------------------------------------------- --------------
  **#8**   **SHELVING & FINISH ACCESSORIES --- Extract From    **NEW
           Floor Plan**                                        EXTRACTION**

  -------- --------------------------------------------------- --------------

**Problem**

Our takeoff had no closet shelving, no closet rods, and no bathroom
accessories. Burton\'s quote included \$292 in closet shelving and \$507
in bath accessories. All of this is extractable by counting closets and
bathrooms on the floor plan.

**New Extraction Rule --- Add to Assumptions Checklist Section 7**

> SHELVING EXTRACTION RULE (new):
>
> WALK-IN CLOSET:
>
> Measure interior perimeter from floor plan.
>
> ShelvingLF = perimeter x 0.75 (3-wall standard coverage)
>
> Default material: 3/4\" x 12\" particle board
>
> Add: 1 double closet rod kit per walk-in
>
> REACH-IN CLOSET (standard bedroom closet):
>
> ShelvingLF = opening width + 6\" return each side
>
> Default: 3/4\" x 12\" PB, 1 single rod per opening
>
> LINEN / PANTRY CLOSET (shelves only, no rod):
>
> ShelfCount = floor(closet height / 12\") (one shelf per foot)
>
> Each shelf LF = opening width
>
> Total ShelvingLF = ShelfCount x opening width
>
> OUTPUT:
>
> Particle Board Shelving 3/4\"x12\" \-- \[LF\] LF -\> \[N\] EA at stock
> lengths
>
> Closet Rod (adjustable) \-- \[N\] EA, sized to opening width
>
> BATHROOM ACCESSORIES (per bathroom type):
>
> Full bath: 1 towel bar (30\") + 1 towel ring + 1 toilet paper holder
>
> Master bath: 2 towel bars (30\") + 1 towel ring + 1 toilet paper
> holder
>
> Half bath: 1 toilet paper holder + 1 small towel ring
>
> OUTPUT:
>
> Towel bars 30\": \[N\] EA
>
> Towel rings: \[N\] EA
>
> Toilet paper holders: \[N\] EA
>
> Note: Finish spec (satin nickel / oil-rubbed bronze etc) = owner
> selection.
>
> Quantities based on \[N\] full baths + \[N\] half baths per floor
> plan.

**Quick Estimate for Burt Residence**

  ------------------------------------------------------------------------
  **Item**                    **Qty**       **Source Logic**
  --------------------------- ------------- ------------------------------
  Towel bars 30\" --- full    4 EA          4 full baths x 1 each
  baths                                     

  Towel bars 30\" --- master  +2 EA         Master bath = double bar
  bath upgrade                              standard

  Towel rings                 5 EA          1 per bath + 1 half bath

  Toilet paper holders        5 EA          1 per toilet --- 5 toilets on
                                            plans

  Closet rods (reach-in)      \~6 EA        Counted from A2/A3 floor plans

  PB Shelving 3/4\"x12\"      \~80-120 LF   6 closets x avg 15 LF each

  Shelf supports / rod        \~14 EA       2-3 per closet, 4 per linen
  brackets                                  
