**STANDARD LIABILITY CLAUSE --- APPEND TO ALL TAKEOFF OUTPUTS**

Add the following to every takeoff document produced by this system:

+-----------------------------------------------------------------------+
| **ESTIMATING LIABILITY NOTICE**                                       |
|                                                                       |
| This material takeoff is produced as an estimating aid only.          |
| Quantities marked \'net count, no waste factor\' reflect calculated   |
| net quantities from plan dimensions. They do NOT include cutting      |
| waste, installation damage, transport loss, or field adjustment       |
| allowances.                                                           |
|                                                                       |
| The General Contractor is solely responsible for: (1) verifying       |
| quantities against field conditions, (2) adding appropriate waste     |
| factors per their practice, (3) confirming material specifications    |
| with the Engineer of Record, and (4) compliance with all applicable   |
| codes.                                                                |
|                                                                       |
| **NO WASTE FACTOR applied to: Rebar, Roof OSB, Subfloor T&G OSB, MDF  |
| Trim, Shelving, Bath Accessories.**                                   |
|                                                                       |
| **WASTE FACTOR INCLUDED in: Wall OSB (12%), Drywall (12%), Concrete   |
| (7%), Insulation (7%), Shingles (12%), Siding (10%).**                |
